sentences: He was an accompanist to singers Sarah Vaughan (in 1979) and Ella Fitzgerald (1989–1994).
He was an accompanist to singers Sarah Vaughan (in 1979) and Ella Fitzgerald (1989–1994).
He was known in the jazz community going back to the 1960s for the albums Strawberry Wine and Summer Night.
